  <h2>Origins</h2>

  <p>Cascading Media, LLC was created on October 23, 2008 by Benjamin Patch while serving with the US Army during his third combat tour in Iraq. The LLC (Limited Liability Company) paperwork was filed over the Internet with the state of Colorado in preparation for Benjamin&#8217;s return to Colorado Springs in early 2009.</p>

