  <p>While still serving as an Intelligence Analyst for 10th Special Forces Group out of Fort Carson, Colorado, Benjamin was also running Cascading Media with any time he could spare. In August 2009, Sergeant Benjamin Patch was honorably discharged from the US Army, completing his six and half years of service, three combat tours to Iraq and a two-year overseas tour in Germany. From that point forward, Benjamin has been running Cascading Media full time.</p>

